insert into diksha_tpd_mapping(uuid,state,district_name,school_name,school_id,status,created_on,updated_on) select uuid,state,district_name,school_name,school_id,status,now(),now() from (SELECT uuid,state,district_name,school_name,school_id,status, row_number() over (partition by uuid,state,district_name,school_name,school_id,status) as rn from diksha_tpd_mapping_temp) sq Where rn =1 on conflict(uuid,school_id) do update set uuid=excluded.uuid,state=excluded.state,district_name=excluded.district_name, school_name=excluded.school_name,school_id=excluded.school_id,status=excluded.status,updated_on=now()
